Enactment of REGULATIONS AMENDING THE ONTARIO HYDRO NUCLEAR FACILITIES
EXCLUSION FROM PART I OF THE CANADA LABOUR CODE REGULATIONS (INDUSTRIAL
RELATIONS)(MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) by replacing therein the outdated
references to the Atomic Energy Control Act with references to the new
Nuclear Safety and Control Act.
